target: input
validations:
  - name: tile_selection
    type: agent_validation
    severity: error
    args:
      rubric: >
        Verify that clicking on the canvas selects the correct tile. In
        select mode, clicking on an enclosure tile should select that
        enclosure and display its information. Clicking on an empty tile
        should deselect any current selection. The selected tile should be
        visually highlighted.
  - name: build_mode_placement
    type: agent_validation
    severity: error
    args:
      rubric: >
        Verify that build mode works for placing enclosures and paths. The
        player should be able to enter build mode via the sidebar, select an
        enclosure type, and click on the map to place it. The enclosure
        should appear at the clicked location. Attempting to place on an
        occupied area should fail silently (no crash, no placement).
  - name: keyboard_shortcuts
    type: agent_validation
    severity: error
    args:
      rubric: >
        Verify that keyboard shortcuts function correctly. P should toggle
        pause, 1/2/4 should change game speed, ESC should return to select
        mode and clear selection, and arrow keys should pan the camera.
        Each shortcut should have an immediate visible effect.
  - name: camera_drag
    type: agent_validation
    severity: error
    args:
      rubric: >
        Verify that clicking and dragging on the map pans the camera. The
        view should follow the mouse movement smoothly. A short click (less
        than 4 pixels of movement) should be treated as a click, not a drag.
        Dragging should not select or deselect entities.
